msgid "Special features in the code editor"
msgstr ""

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/edit.rst:711
# 88a0f5d93789405f82ab9184be383d36
msgid "The calibre HTML editor is very powerful. It has many features that make editing of HTML (and CSS) easier."
