msgid "The text inside bold, italic and heading tags is made bold/italic"
msgstr ""

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/edit.rst:720
# 277c2bd7e4454942b644dec07536b517
msgid "As you move your cursor through the HTML, the matching HTML tags are highlighted"
msgstr ""

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/edit.rst:722
# 29280ffe0d8543aba7272a6bd596675e
msgid "Invalid HTML is highlighted with a red underline"
msgstr ""

#: ../../home/kovid/work/calibre/manual/edit.rst:723
# 45aca4a6f4784e6a9f05f79a1e2d559f
msgid "Spelling errors in the text inside HTML tags and attributes such as title are highlighted. The spell checking is language aware, based on the value of the lang attribute of the current tag and the overall book language."
